name: v0.2.0
body:
- Accept inputs via STDIN (#16)
- Support Fluentd sub-second time(event time) (#20)
- Add time_format `unix` (#25)

name: v0.1.5
body:
- Select a host to send at random from DNS multiple response.
  - Previously, selected by Go's DNS resolver algorithm (based on RFC6724).

name: v0.1.4
body: Always convert to int64 if specified as 'integer' in Types directive.

name: v0.1.1
body: - Added time parser. (Includes default setting bug. Please use v0.1.2)

- LTSV, JSON format parser.
- Send messags to multiple server by round-robin.
